Package: weimea
Type: Package
Title: Weighted mean of species attributes
Version: 0.15
Date: 2014-11-07
Author: David Zeleny
Maintainer: David Zeleny <zeleny.david@gmail.com>
Description: Calculates weighted mean of species attributes, and
    offers other functions handling weighted mean, e.g. when related to sample
    attributes. Examples of use: community weighted mean of species traits,
    mean Ellenberg indicator values etc.
Imports:
    vegan,
    ape
Depends:
    vegan,
    ape
License: GPL-2
